# Takeaways

- Sometimes it is better to relax a bit and keep something in reserve.
- Be careful of accelerating hard at the start of a project. It can feel more productive than it really is.
- Hugh Jackman is a wonderful and compelling storyteller. Especially if he managed to make the 85% rule up on the spot.
